[[Bebe Rexha]] is an American singer, songwriter, and record producer. Bebe was selected as the fifth among Top 10 Stars to Watch Out For in 2018 at [[Watchmojo.com]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Top 10 Stars to Watch Out For in 2018 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u_OpqDQynTc |website=youtube}}</ref> She has won 18 awards from 47 nominations.

