==ASCAP Awards==
The [[American Society of Composers, Authors and Publishers#Awards|ASCAP Awards]] honor the songwriters and publishers of the American Society of Composers, Authors and Publishers' most performed songs.<ref>{{cite web|title=32nd Annual ASCAP Pop Music Awards|url=https://www.ascap.com/press/pressroom/popawards.aspx|publisher=ASCAP}}</ref> Rexha has received two ASCAP London Music Awards and one ASCAP Pop Music Award.

