==BMI Awards==
The [[BMI Award|BMI Awards]] are held annually by [[Broadcast Music, Inc.]] to award songwriters in various genres, including country and pop.<ref>{{cite web|title=Oscar-Winning Composer Alexandre Desplat Honored as BMI Icon at 2015 Film/TV Awards |url=http://www.bmi.com/news/entry/2015_bmi_film_tv_awards |publisher=[[Broadcast Music, Inc.]] |accessdate=June 24, 2018 |date=May 14, 2015 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617070006/http://www.bmi.com/news/entry/2015_bmi_film_tv_awards |archivedate=June 17, 2015 |df= }}</ref> Rexha has received three BMI London Awards, two BMI Pop Award, and two BMI R&B/Hip-Hop Awards. 

